text:
Producer?
Why are you in such a hurry?

Sorry Meguru! It seems there was a miscommunication,
and your turn is coming up soon!

Sorry for the rush, especially in indoor shoes
with heels, but can you run to the studio?
Don't worry, leave it to me!

Even with unstable shoes,
singing and dancing perfectly is my job!
...Wait, this isn't the time for saying that!
